1
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:08,920
‪SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:42,560
‪ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‪QUEEN CHU</i>‪ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,160
Is all this really necessary?

4
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,280
Weren't you afraid
she'd actually kill you?

5
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,880
Kill me?

6
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,160
It would plunge the court into chaos.

7
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,760
Her Highness was just trying
to humiliate me

8
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,440
and vent her spite.

9
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:10,080
So, are you breaking the pact
and making her your enemy?

10
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,040
The pact?

11
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,640
Since when has she ever cared for that?

12
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:19,320
She handed the Imperial Guard Tally
to a nobody from the Xie Family.

13
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,640
Is that her idea of sincerity?

14
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,160
If you had held the Tally,

15
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,360
she would have had
even less chance of survival.

16
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,440
Xiao Xun cannot die.

17
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,000
At least not yet.

18
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,120
Why?

19
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,000
Is this the fallback you mentioned?

20
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:06,000
The late Emperor's final edict.

21
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:09,080
Xiao Xun was the designated heir.

22
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:13,040
It was due to unforeseen complications

23
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:17,080
that the crown passed to Xiao Yu.

24
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,720
{\an8}‪ONE DAY EARLIER

25
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,640
{\an8}Your Highness.

26
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:28,000
My gates have been so deserted

27
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,760
that even the sparrows
give this place a wide berth.

28
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,120
It is truly rare
that you would actually reach out

29
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,360
to Tie Ying.

30
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,400
Your Highness, have you ever heard

31
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,040
of greatness biding its time
in the depths?

32
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,920
Mr. Deng, are you here

33
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:52,880
to teach me fortune-reading?

34
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:57,400
It is a pity
that your judgment has failed you

35
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:03,400
because there is no greatness
to be found here.

36
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:08,960
I am naught but a lamb to the slaughter.

37
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,320
No.

38
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:13,360
I am here to show you

39
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:17,440
a path to Xiaonan.

40
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:22,000
Also a path to help reclaim
your former glory.

41
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,840
Why help me?

42
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:42,400
The imperial court has always been
a treacherous place

43
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,680
of shifting tides.

44
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,720
I don't dare to stake everything
on a single play.

45
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:50,040
That was true then as it is now.

46
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:56,680
I am aiding you because I hold
a far more compelling hand.

47
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,960
This is the late Emperor's final edict.

48
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:09,360
You were the one
meant to inherit the throne.

49
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,760
Indeed, Your Highness.

50
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,560
This is a forgery.

51
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:19,160
- You…
- But I have the true one, too.

52
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,240
His Majesty has barely
ascended the throne.

53
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,040
Aren't you afraid
of being branded a rebel?

54
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:31,000
Precision is required to strike,
and clarity is needed to lead.

55
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:36,040
I aligned with Chu Zhao for a promise

56
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:40,920
she later broke, prompting my shift
to Your Highness.

57
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:44,640
My goal has stayed the same throughout.

58
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:48,480
Are you aware now, Your Highness?

59
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:56,120
When I claim my destiny,
the seat of Grand Mentor shall be yours.

60
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,200
Mr. Deng, you have a visitor.

61
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:22,680
So you've prepared your own coffin?

62
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,920
How kind of you to save
the court the expense.

63
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:29,000
Such prime golden-thread nanmu.

64
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,280
Not really.

65
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,520
It was bestowed by Her Highness.

66
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:37,160
I heard when the late Emperor
crushed the old dynasty,

67
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:40,840
the fallen ruler used this very timber

68
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,160
to immolate himself for his state.

69
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,400
I spoke inappropriately.

70
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:49,800
What brings you here, exactly?

71
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,840
There is a matter

72
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:59,280
I'm hoping you could shed some light on.

73
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,160
Do you know

74
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:11,040
Her Highness has besieged
the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan?

75
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,880
Of course.

76
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:17,640
Do you also know
that Xiao Xun has escaped?

77
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,720
I do.

78
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,360
Do you know

79
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,760
who let him go?

80
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,720
It was me.

81
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:40,480
Your honesty is quite touching.

82
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:45,680
Such an act proves
you have turned against Her Highness.

83
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:51,480
But have you considered
the weight of this coffin?

84
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:57,840
Can you carry it alone?

85
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:02,880
You came through the midnight rain
only for this?

86
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,600
I was wondering

87
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:08,040
if I were the one
letting Xiao Xun walk free,

88
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,680
would she have brought

89
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:14,600
this coffin
through my Xie Clan's front door?

90
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,160
Mr. Deng,

91
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:20,400
playing with fire
without a clan's backing is folly.

92
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:24,480
Beware you don't get burned.

93
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,920
I've long heard your mastery
of the board is unrivaled.

94
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,560
Might I invite you for a round?

95
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,679
It would be my honor.

96
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:44,280
{\an8}‪MILITARY CAMP OF YUNZHONG PREFECTURE

97
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:48,280
General, the Northern Desert forces
know our defenses inside out.

98
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:50,360
They even have the exact locations
of our hidden sentries.

99
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,560
We must have a traitor.

100
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,960
Report!

101
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,200
Report. Urgent news from the Capital.

102
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,800
Her Highness faces impeachment.

103
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,360
The heir to the Lord of Xiaonan
has fled by night.

104
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,840
Imperial Guard Commander Fu Jiu
is wounded.

105
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,440
Is Jiu's condition severe?

106
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:09,080
Word is the Imperial Physicians
have consulted, and he is out of danger.

107
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,680
Is Zhao safe and sound?

108
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,680
Her Highness is unharmed.

109
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:20,960
Xiao Xun fled back to Xiaonan,
and now the Northern Desert invades

110
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,880
with such intimate knowledge
of our defenses.

111
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:29,000
Could it be a betrayal from within?

112
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,800
Pass the order.

113
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:34,400
The Third Battalion
is to redeploy to Langya Valley.

114
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,960
The Fifth is to set an ambush
at Yingzui Cliff.

115
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:38,000
Adjust the defensive line as planned.

116
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:43,120
Position the hidden troops
and wait for them to take the bait.

117
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,000
- Understood!
- Understood!

118
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,560
General!

119
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,600
General, what is this malady?

120
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:57,960
It worsens by the day.

121
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,640
Even medicine offers no relief.

122
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,120
It's nothing.

123
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:06,200
I'll lead the charge tomorrow.

124
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,320
No. You can barely stand.

125
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,680
This is an order.

126
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,120
An order is an order.

127
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,000
Yes.

128
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:24,840
Your Highness,

129
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:28,400
Mr. Xie has been recovering here
for three days now.

130
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:32,160
Though your title leaves
few who dare to criticize you,

131
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:35,440
the boundaries of decorum remain.

132
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:39,480
I fear the idle tongues outside
are already beginning to wag.

133
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,400
Since I entered these imperial walls,

134
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:47,160
when have the rumors ever stopped?

135
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:54,000
The Censorate is bent on branding me
as "a hen ruling the roost".

136
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,560
Besides,

137
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,640
his injuries are deep.

138
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:05,600
I won't risk leaving him to others.

139
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:08,240
Is it because Your Highness
has feelings for him

140
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:12,120
that you refused to marry Mr. Xiao?

141
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:19,320
After all our time together,
is that truly how you see me?

142
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:22,840
No. I spoke out of turn.

143
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:24,320
Please, do not be angry.

144
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:32,440
Every string in this palace
must be mine to pull.

145
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,680
But he is more than just a pawn.

146
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,000
He is…

147
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:44,680
different.

148
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,480
How?

149
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,040
I used him,

150
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:55,120
and yet, I trust him
more than anyone else.

151
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,120
Regardless,

152
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:05,920
he is different.

153
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,680
Urgent news from the frontier!

154
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:13,000
The Northern Desert has attacked Yunzhong.

155
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:17,520
No.

156
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,400
My report was a forgery.

157
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,080
How could it possibly be real?

158
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,440
Since Her Highness forged the report

159
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:36,160
of collusion between the Lord of Xiaonan
and the Northern Desert

160
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:39,920
and tried to drag my family
into this using Pine Soot Ink,

161
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,720
she should have been prepared

162
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:44,120
for the possibility that her scheme
could spark a real war.

163
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,200
Playing the game,

164
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,600
one must always keep a backup plan.

165
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,480
You look refined,

166
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,240
yet your style of play is ruthless.

167
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,800
You flatter me.

168
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:02,280
I just dislike wasting time.

169
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,880
However,

170
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:10,640
patience is the true essence
of Weiqi games.

171
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:22,800
At the start of this match,
you were full of confidence,

172
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:24,520
weren't you?

173
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:31,080
But look at it now.

174
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,920
The situation has changed.

175
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:45,200
Do my skills meet with your approval?

176
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,920
Your skill…

177
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:54,840
- is exceptional.
- Good.

178
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,600
Since you enjoy watching,

179
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,960
I shall set several games in motion.

180
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:02,720
But a board too full
leaves no clear opening.

181
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:06,960
Beware lest you find no way out.

182
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,480
You're awake.

183
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,880
Are you in any pain?

184
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,640
I failed my mission.

185
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,120
I've dragged you down with me

186
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:53,360
and gotten you injured.

187
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:59,080
Deng Yi sent his men
to issue orders at the docks,

188
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:01,640
which gave Xiao Xun
a chance to escape by water.

189
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:06,200
I thought it was foolproof.

190
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,640
Yet…

191
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:14,080
The game at court is never that simple.

192
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:16,800
Such is the nature of power.

193
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:18,800
Tell me.

194
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:20,520
How do you want me to repay this debt?

195
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,840
I can grant you one wish.

196
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,840
I've never believed in divinity.

197
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,320
I have no wishes.

198
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:39,320
Then is there nothing you wish to achieve?

199
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:45,520
No.

200
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:48,640
Very well.

201
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:51,400
Then let the debt stand for now.

202
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:55,440
When you decide what you want,
just come to me.

203
00:17:08,079 --> 00:17:10,720
With your skills,
you shouldn't be this badly hurt.

204
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:15,040
What really happened that day?

205
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:19,800
Tie Ying

206
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:23,200
used hidden weapons.

207
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:26,720
I let my guard down and got ambushed.

208
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:28,160
Just as I thought.

209
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:31,120
They only resort
to such despicable tricks.

210
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,280
Last night, I saw you having a nightmare.

211
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,880
You seemed burdened by something.

212
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:44,240
As you said,

213
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:47,880
everyone has their own secrets.

214
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:52,360
True. But I shared mine with you.

215
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:55,960
You mean that dream?

216
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:07,520
Alright.

217
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,360
As an exchange,

218
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:11,880
I'll tell you a secret.

219
00:18:19,960 --> 00:18:20,840
Actually…

220
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:26,600
I…

221
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:40,080
CAPITAL

222
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:58,600
I once sneaked a bite of the jujube cakes
you got for your father

223
00:18:59,120 --> 00:19:00,160
and paid for it with a beating.

224
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:03,640
Thank you for sharing that.

225
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:06,120
It's just…

226
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:09,680
I'll never make that again.

227
00:19:16,120 --> 00:19:17,080
No matter.

228
00:19:18,560 --> 00:19:20,520
I never liked those pastries anyway.

229
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:26,880
I was thinking of making you
something else to eat.

230
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,040
Sounds good.

231
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:58,440
Jiu, my hairpin is a bit askew.

232
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,400
Fix it for me, would you?

233
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:46,920
Good, right?

234
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:50,040
Six hours at the stove,
steamer after steamer,

235
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:51,640
all for a flawless batch.

236
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:56,480
It's truly the finest delicacy
in the world.

237
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:58,960
You should've mixed the filling properly.

238
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:01,600
The ratio of lard has to be exact.

239
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:03,400
Too little or too much ruins it.

240
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:05,960
I see.

241
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,960
My father always said

242
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:10,960
too little makes it dry
and too much makes it greasy.

243
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,520
It's my fault.

244
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:27,480
I have been away from Yunzhong for so long

245
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,080
that I have forgotten

246
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,360
the recipe.

247
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,360
In fact,

248
00:22:40,280 --> 00:22:41,440
I was never very skilled

249
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:45,320
at making these pastries to begin with.

250
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:52,800
Father, see? I made it.

251
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:54,640
I finally mastered jujube cakes.

252
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:58,320
Well done.

253
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:02,240
Just try not to sneak
the filling next time.

254
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:10,880
<i>Father, don't scare me.</i>
<i>I just missed my mother.</i>

255
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:13,800
I didn't grow up by her side,
so I wanted to take a look.

256
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:17,320
To look at the sights she saw
and walk the lanes she walked.

257
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,640
If Mother were still alive,

258
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:22,360
she wouldn't want me
to be an obedient girl.

259
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,560
She wouldn't be as arrogant as you.

260
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:27,560
<i>She would care about my feelings.</i>

261
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:32,400
<i>Yeah. You're the undefeated God of War.</i>

262
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:34,320
<i>You're the esteemed Guard General.</i>

263
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:36,440
<i>You're busy protecting frontier people.</i>

264
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:38,840
<i>You're busy forging your fame.</i>

265
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,040
<i>You're too busy</i>

266
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:43,480
<i>to ask your daughter</i>
<i>what she really wants!</i>

267
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:51,560
Missing someone
is nothing to be ashamed of.

268
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:56,560
And neither is being homesick.

269
00:24:17,360 --> 00:24:18,880
During the years I spent
by your father's side,

270
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,400
he seemed truly content.

271
00:24:23,280 --> 00:24:24,800
He kept himself busy,

272
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:28,800
but whenever he got rare spices
from the Western Regions,

273
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:32,080
he would tuck them away
in the room at the southern courtyard.

274
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,640
When he went out on patrol,

275
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:37,000
if he saw a lovely sprig of blossoms,

276
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:41,520
he would bring it back
to plant in that courtyard.

277
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:46,360
He told me it was where you once lived,

278
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:48,560
and so he kept it in order
for your return.

279
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:56,080
Chu Zhao.

280
00:24:59,080 --> 00:25:00,320
Your father never blamed you

281
00:25:01,600 --> 00:25:02,720
for your leaving.

282
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,880
He only wanted to know

283
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:07,800
whether you were doing well.

284
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:11,440
He has missed you, that's all.

285
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:17,480
You don't have to respond to any of this.

286
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:20,400
These are his feelings to carry.

287
00:25:22,360 --> 00:25:23,720
So please don't be too hard on yourself.

288
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:28,440
No one needs to be forgiven.

289
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:31,000
Actually,

290
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,560
I miss him terribly too

291
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,160
and everything about the desert.

292
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:48,160
He is a man of stern discipline

293
00:25:49,280 --> 00:25:50,360
yet with a tender heart.

294
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:54,400
Much like you.

295
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:05,280
The first time he took me
to the desert poplar forest,

296
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:08,280
he said every withered branch there

297
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,840
was fighting desperately to stay alive,

298
00:26:11,520 --> 00:26:13,360
which is what shaped
this timeless landscape.

299
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:16,800
Dying is easy.

300
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:22,080
Living takes true strength.

301
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,360
Jiu.

302
00:26:28,280 --> 00:26:29,240
My apologies.

303
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,120
I've said too much.

304
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:32,920
Not at all.

305
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:38,520
I'm glad to hear you speak your mind.

306
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,200
It's late and cold.

307
00:26:44,320 --> 00:26:45,400
Please get some rest, Your Highness.

308
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:47,920
Thank you

309
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:51,600
for telling me about my father

310
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:54,960
and for sharing your past with me.

311
00:26:56,840 --> 00:26:57,680
You are welcome.

312
00:26:59,600 --> 00:27:01,000
Consider it repayment

313
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:03,680
for that pastry.

314
00:27:07,240 --> 00:27:10,680
Then please take this box
of red bean cakes.

315
00:27:12,120 --> 00:27:13,160
I appreciate it.

316
00:27:15,080 --> 00:27:16,720
What I said today still stands.

317
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,160
From now on,

318
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:24,840
whatever wish you hold,
you may ask it of me.

319
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:27,440
Come fire or high water,

320
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,520
I will see it fulfilled.

321
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:37,560
I honor my promises and never renege.

322
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,800
Alright. I understand.

323
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:45,520
Report!

324
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:47,920
Report!

325
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:51,280
Your Highness, urgent news from Yunzhong.

326
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:52,880
<i>The Northern Desert invaded yesterday.</i>

327
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:55,360
<i>General Chu drove them back,</i>
<i>but collapsed shortly after.</i>

328
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,560
<i>He hasn't woken up.</i>

329
00:27:58,960 --> 00:28:00,760
General. The enemy has withdrawn!

330
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:03,720
Exactly as you predicted.

331
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:06,320
Your foresight secured our victory.

332
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,400
General.

333
00:28:27,600 --> 00:28:30,720
{\an8}‪LORD OF XIAONAN'S MANOR

334
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,720
Father.

335
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:50,800
Are you hurt?

336
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:54,520
You may not know,

337
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:58,640
but Chu Ling's daughter
seeks to finish me off for good.

338
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,840
Chu Ling's daughter?

339
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:03,680
The one who refused to marry you

340
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:05,240
and only ever wanted
to be the Grand Princess?

341
00:29:07,080 --> 00:29:09,200
The throne changes and chaos follows.

342
00:29:10,080 --> 00:29:12,480
We and Yunzhong hold each other in check.

343
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:15,080
The Xie Clan of Gaoyang
eyes us with greed.

344
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:19,040
Yet she moved first to purge
our army in the Capital,

345
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:22,720
then used your plight
to build her power in the court.

346
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:27,240
Such methods are truly masterful.

347
00:29:27,320 --> 00:29:31,200
This upheaval plunges
the Capital into chaos.

348
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:34,280
- Perhaps we…
- The essence of alchemy lies

349
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:36,400
within the mastery of fire.

350
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:38,960
When the Yellow Emperor
forged his cauldron,

351
00:29:39,040 --> 00:29:41,400
the Loong's roar emerged after 49 days.

352
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:45,080
When the alchemists refined mercury,
the rosy aura condensed after 81 nights.

353
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:47,680
It all comes down to the precise moment.

354
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:51,440
Opening the cauldron
before completion risks failure.

355
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,960
‪LORD OF XIAONAN, XIAO HONG

356
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:57,240
You must be weary from the road.

357
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:58,880
Get some rest.

358
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:02,000
Yes.

359
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:17,560
General Chu Ling

360
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:21,200
shall be held negligent
for the Northern Desert's incursion.

361
00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:23,960
Yes, they breached our frontiers,

362
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,960
but it is also true General Chu
led them into a void.

363
00:30:27,040 --> 00:30:30,120
No reward for his merit,
yet only a trial for his fault?

364
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:32,200
Since he took command,

365
00:30:32,280 --> 00:30:35,280
victory has been his solemn duty.

366
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:37,240
Had Yunzhong fallen,

367
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:39,120
the consequences
would've been catastrophic.

368
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:41,520
Merit cannot offset such a grave failing.

369
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:43,280
Your Majesty,

370
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,440
Chu Ling has been lax
in disciplining his troops

371
00:30:46,080 --> 00:30:47,440
and must be held to account.

372
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:51,520
- Seconded.
- Seconded.

373
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:55,800
Chamberlain, your concern
for the state is commendable.

374
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:57,400
But I must ask this.

375
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,920
No sooner had Xiao Xun
fled back to Xiaonan,

376
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:03,240
than the invasion happened.

377
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,200
Is this striking coincidence

378
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,920
proof of collusion from within?

379
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:11,880
Your Highness reminded me of something.

380
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:13,840
As I recall,

381
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:16,120
Mr. Deng argued most fervently
for Xiao Xun's pardon,

382
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:18,040
claiming it was to appease

383
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:20,360
the Lord of Xiaonan.

384
00:31:21,040 --> 00:31:25,000
Such impeccable timing
for a show of mercy.

385
00:31:26,320 --> 00:31:27,800
Watch your words, Mr. Xie.

386
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:32,680
His Majesty decreed
Xiao Xun's pardon and return.

387
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:35,640
Who am I to challenge the throne?

388
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:41,280
Word has it you've set your sights

389
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:43,960
on Xiao Xun's residence.

390
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:47,400
It is a place of great vantage.

391
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:50,520
Better to use it than waste it.

392
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:53,600
His Majesty, in his infinite mercy,
bestowed it upon me.

393
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:54,760
What?

394
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:58,560
- You wish for it as well?
- Enough.

395
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:02,120
With the Northern Desert encroaching,
our priority is to steady the troops.

396
00:32:03,280 --> 00:32:04,720
As for the cancer within…

397
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:12,160
I shall see for myself

398
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:17,320
who is so desperate to usher in the enemy.

399
00:32:21,440 --> 00:32:22,280
I am weary.

400
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,800
Should you have no other matters,
you may take your leave.

401
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,560
- We bid farewell to Your Majesty
- We bid farewell to Your Majesty

402
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:30,360
- and Your Highness.
- and Your Highness.

403
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:57,040
Who would have thought Xie Yanfang

404
00:32:57,920 --> 00:33:00,160
would show his hand so brazenly?

405
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:03,000
Since he dared tell you

406
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:06,680
he would bring
the Grand Princess a true war,

407
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,760
he clearly fears nothing,

408
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:10,800
knowing we lack the evidence

409
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:13,240
to move against him.

410
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,000
Indeed.

411
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:20,880
The very fact he said it proves
he has a contingency plan in place.

412
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,560
Even if we sent men to investigate now,

413
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,960
they would find nothing.

414
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:29,080
Xie Yanfang is guarded
like an iron fortress.

415
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:31,840
But even the tightest defense has a flaw.

416
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:36,040
Why not start by digging
into his place in Gaoyang?

417
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,160
When he came to the Capital,

418
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:41,520
he brought all his men with him.

419
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:45,840
The rest at the Gaoyang estate
are of no consequence.

420
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,520
You are right, though.

421
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:50,080
To strike at the heart of the threat,

422
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:53,400
one must first brave the lion's den.

423
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:58,840
Shao You.

424
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,640
Send men to Gaoyang at once.

425
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:08,400
Understood.

426
00:34:12,239 --> 00:34:13,239
Mr. Xie,

427
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:18,440
better mind your moves in this game.

428
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:22,320
{\an8}PRINCE XIAO XUN'S RESIDENCE

429
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:26,520
Move more to the left. Higher.

430
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,199
XIE RESIDENCE

431
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:30,320
That's it. Get down.

432
00:34:32,560 --> 00:34:34,000
With that plaque in place,

433
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:36,440
the whole estate seems brighter.

434
00:34:36,520 --> 00:34:39,440
Mr. Xie, rumors have it

435
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:42,040
Guard General Chu Ling's negligence
allowed the breach.

436
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:47,000
Do you think he'd be like Xiao Xun,
colluding with the enemy?

437
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:51,600
If Xiao could survive such dire straits,
so can he.

438
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:54,480
Having spent years at the frontier
with an undefeated record,

439
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,880
the prestige he holds among the people

440
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,240
can not be undone by a single lapse
in judgment.

441
00:35:00,040 --> 00:35:02,520
We may have orchestrated the invasion,

442
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:07,760
but his swift tactical shift
lured the enemy to Xinggu Pass

443
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,520
and secured a total victory.

444
00:35:11,040 --> 00:35:14,400
Many now laud his braveness and mind.

445
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:20,840
It seems we've only served
to further his renown.

446
00:35:22,080 --> 00:35:23,080
True.

447
00:35:23,160 --> 00:35:24,840
Just as you are renowned
throughout the land.

448
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:27,040
Though away from court for years,

449
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,960
your foundation remains unshakable.

450
00:35:30,160 --> 00:35:31,000
No.

451
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:33,960
He and I…

452
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,600
have never been the same.

453
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:39,840
Since the estate is renovated,

454
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,280
send for Yanlai.

455
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:48,440
Tell him it is the Master's command
that he return at once.

456
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:51,440
He's always been at odds with your family.

457
00:35:51,520 --> 00:35:52,360
Why this?

458
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:54,320
I am merely curious.

459
00:35:57,520 --> 00:35:59,680
After five years, does the hound…

460
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:03,400
still know its leash?

461
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:07,360
Blessings and calamities coexist.

462
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:10,200
Great fortune is accompanied
by great danger.

463
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,040
‪CHU TANG, COUSIN OF CHU ZHAO

464
00:36:11,120 --> 00:36:13,720
This title may not prove to be

465
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:16,600
a shield for the Chu Family.

466
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:21,840
Of course,
I am grateful for Uncle's care years ago.

467
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:23,760
It's just…

468
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,720
Should I fall from this height,

469
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:31,880
as family, you will
inevitably be implicated.

470
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:37,160
So, you'd better plot your own course.

471
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:40,280
Zhao, no need to test me.

472
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:43,800
From the day you attained this title,

473
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:51,120
the Chu Family rises and falls with you.

474
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:53,800
Very well.

475
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:56,960
Then,

476
00:37:06,240 --> 00:37:09,360
from now on,
I shall maneuver in the light,

477
00:37:10,040 --> 00:37:11,360
while you operate in the shadows.

478
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:15,160
I'll be your fortress,
and you'll be my reach.

479
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:19,360
If we win, we shall share
in glory and splendor.

480
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,320
If we fail…

481
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:31,360
I am yours to command.

482
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:35,280
Please keep faith with your pledge.

483
00:37:36,040 --> 00:37:37,120
After this tea,

484
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:39,480
there is no turning back.

485
00:37:47,200 --> 00:37:48,400
<i>Now that I depart the Capital,</i>

486
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:52,960
<i>I must rally every available ally</i>
<i>to hold the court for me.</i>

